			<content translate="true">&lt;P ALIGN="LEFT"&gt;&lt;B&gt;Situation: &lt;/B&gt;A parent is concerned that he didn’t give enough of his time and attention to his child during the child’s first two years and now it’s too late.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P ALIGN="LEFT"&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P ALIGN="LEFT"&gt;&lt;B&gt;Possible Response:&lt;/B&gt; Tell the father that it's never too late. Development is flexible, and his child can still benefit from additional parental interaction.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P ALIGN="LEFT"&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P ALIGN="LEFT"&gt;Is this the best response?&lt;/P&gt;</content>
